-- Billionaire Lisin’s Freight One May Buy Evraz Transport Unit
-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 2012-06-23T08:34:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-23/billionaire-lisin-s-freight-one-may-buy-evraz-transport-unit.html
Russian billionaire  Vladimir Lisin ’s
OAO Freight One is studying the possible acquisition of a
transportation unit of London-listed steelmaker  Evraz Plc (EVR) , 
spokesman Dmitry Baukov said by phone from Moscow.  Evraz, part-owned by billionaire Roman Abramovich, said
June 19 it may sell its EvrazTrans unit.  To contact the reporter on this story:
